Class StarSystemScene

  • java.lang.Object

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TestSystemScene
    public class StarSystemScene
extends SmartScene
    Sun - AxialTilt = 0 - plane of ecliptic = x,y Planet - RotationAxis Z - put in a Group - apply AxialTilt around Y to the Group - apply Orbit to Group - add to another group - Inclination of Orbit - rotate around Z for longitude of ascending node - set the start point on the orbit to the argument of Perihelion
    Author:
    Roland Kastner
